'''休奇耶'''（{{lang-ru|Щу́чье}}，意即「[[狗魚|狗魚]]」）是[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]][[庫爾干州|庫爾干州]]西部的一個城市，距[[庫爾干|庫爾干]]180公里。2002年人口10,602人。

休奇耶于1750年建立，1945年正式建市。大约14%的俄罗斯化学武器储存在休奇耶<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2009/05/27/world/europe/27russia.html?ref=world|work=The New York Times|title=In Siberia, the Death Knell of a Complex Holding a Deadly Stockpile|first=Clifford J.|last=Levy|date=2009-05-27|accessdate=2010-04-09|archive-date=2022-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220224125544/https://www.nytimes.com/2009/05/27/world/europe/27russia.html?ref=world|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年，許多存儲在休奇耶的化学武器被销毁。<ref>{{Cite web|last=Rao |first= Hamid Ali |date=2015-11-20 |title=Remarks at the Closure of Shchuchye Chemical Weapons Destruction Facility, Kurganskaya Oblast, Russian Federation |publisher=Organisation for the Prohibition of Chemical Weapons |url=https://www.opcw.org/fileadmin/OPCW/DDG/DDG_Remarks_Shchuchye_Closure.pdf |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170714102943/https://www.opcw.org/fileadmin/OPCW/DDG/DDG_Remarks_Shchuchye_Closure.pdf |archive-date=2017-07-14 |url-status=live }}</ref>
